author: Jonathan Shieber
title: Tyto Care raises $50 million as it looks to buy and build new services during COVID-19 demand surge
description: Tyto Care, the provider of a home health diagnostic device and telemedicine consultation app, said it has raised $50 million in a new round of funding. The round was led by Insight Partners, Olive Tree Ventures, and Qualcomm Ventures, according to a statement…
